<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.forums.chaoticdreams.org/viewtopic.php?t=6870&amp;p=73210#p73210"><![CDATA[
As the title says, I would like to know which weapons return in the new ChaosUT.<br />I personally feel like all the weapons from the first ChaosUT should return, but not more.<br />ChaosUT2 Evolution has too many weapons imo<br /><br />Weapons I like:<br />Bastard Sword<br />Crossbow (all ammo types)<br />CAS12 Shotgun (all ammo types)<br />CUT Utility Gun<br />C.U.T.T.E.R. (definitely)<br />Proximity Mines + The Claw<br />RPB Bullets for the sniper<br />Turret and Vortex <br />(Turret should be bigger and stronger tho. It is incredibly easy to kill him in both UT's. I prefer him using the shock rifle instead of a minigun tbh and the rockets should fire as frequently as in UT99)<br /><br />Weapons I dislike (or I simply never use them because they are boring):<br />CPP<br />Enhanced Rail Delivery Weapon (aka ERDW)<br /><br />Just saying ChaosUT2004 feels a little to spammy. I simply prefer the UT99 Chaos, but that's just my opinion <img src="http://www.forums.chaoticdreams.org/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":-)" title="Smile" /><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.forums.chaoticdreams.org/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2759">Netzpatron</a> — Wed Jul 27, 2016 1:58 pm — Replies 7 — Views 1060</p><hr />
]]></content>
